<topic class="Popup" template="Default" status="Under Construction" lasteditedby="Adam" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Indexer</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">Indexer</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">An </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Indexer</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> is a cam device with an input and output-shaft. When the Input-shaft (cam) rotates continuously, the output-shaft &apos;indexes&apos; progressively. After a number of index motions, the output shaft returns to its original position. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Some definitions that are used with Indexers:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">NUMBER-OF-STOPS</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: number-of-indexes to rotate the output-shaft one time.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">INDEX-ANGLE</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> the angle that the output-shaft rotates with each index</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">Index Angle [degrees] = 360 / Number-of-Stops.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">INDEX-PERIOD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">: The rotation, in degrees, of the input-shaft to complete the INDEX-ANGLE.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">DWELL PERIOD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">:</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> The rotation, in degrees, of the input-shaft to complete the DWELL. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box2" style="text-align:center;"><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">INDEX PERIOD + DWELL PERIOD</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true"> = 360</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">°</text><text styleclass="Popup Box2" translate="true">. </text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
